reviewText: ONLY ONE VIEW ..SO I WILL NOT BE PURCHASING ANY MORE ..LIVING ART DVDS ..ONLY REASON IT GOT ONE IS FOR ART AND SOUND
Great video!  Very peaceful and calming.

I owned a copy and purchased more for friends.  I find it most relaxing and allows me to "go to anther place".
Excellent condition, excellent service.
Absolutely would recommend it to others.
a light and breezy way of bringing the beach home. add the lemonade, hot dogs and s'mores and you've got it made.

I have collected alot of these for my massage business and this one plus the two other they produced, waterfall and ocean night are great.  They are high definition, loop and the image choices are nice.  I would recommend this one and the other two, moonlight ocean, and rocky mountain waterfall.  Having lived in Hawaii over 6 years, they are the best I have found so far.  Five stars, for all three, including this one.
